    <description>Making another zone with suspended timers for everyone would be a big problem imo. Right now, if you're in a guild and enter your guild hall, it's all fine because it's a instanced zone. Any lag in there is only going to effect those that decided to go there and sit around.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Now imagine if they made the guild lobby buff suspended for example. Imagine the crowding. The zone would be insanely laggy. No one would ever be in pok. They would simply make the guild lobby the new PoK. And of course people would want banks in there, more vendors, stones to all the places, etc. Think about the size differences.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Just food for thought.</description>
